VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT create_engine\s*\(\s*["'](?:postgresql|mysql|sqlite|mssql|oracle)[^"']*://[^"']*:[^"'@]{6,}@
WHEN EXPR MISSING:os\.environ|getenv|config\.|settings\.
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects hardcoded database credentials in SQLAlchemy connection strings.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Hardcoded Database Connection String.
